1. Install new OS X Lion
2. upgrade it to Mavericks
3. install [homebrew][brew]
  * installs git version 1.9.3?
4. install command line tools

```
$ brew doctor
Your system is ready to brew.
```

5. install brew packages
	1. update git to 2.0.3+
	2.

6. install [homebrew-cask][cask]
```
$ brew install caskroom/cask/brew-cask
$ brew cask update # creates Caskroom, requiring admin password.
```

  [brew]: http://brew.sh
  [cask]: https://github.com/caskroom/homebrew-cask
